function.name: single_card_for_hearthstone
function.description: This is the subfunction for tool "hearthstone", you can use this tool.The description of this function is: "Returns card by name or ID. This may return more then one card if they share the same name. Loatheb returns both the card and the boss."

name.description: The name or ID of the card. Example values: Ysera, EX1_572.

callback.description: Request data to be returned as a JsonP callback.

collectible.description: Set this to 1 to only return collectible cards.

locale.description: What locale to use in the response. Default locale is enUS. Available locales: enUS, enGB, deDE, esES, esMX, frFR, itIT, koKR, plPL, ptBR, ruRU, zhCN, zhTW, jaJP, thTH.

function.name: all_cards_for_hearthstone
function.description: This is the subfunction for tool "hearthstone", you can use this tool.The description of this function is: "Returns all available Hearthstone cards including non collectible cards."

attack.description: Return only cards with a certain attack.

durability.description: Return only cards with a certain durability.

health.description: Return only cards with a certain health.

cost.description: Return only cards of a certain cost.
